log
@Remove SHARED_ONLY from all CPAN Perl ports and the cpan and perl MODULES.
Add WANTLIB+=perl and PKG_ARCH=* as appropriate.
@
text
@# $OpenBSD: Makefile,v 1.22 2013/03/11 11:41:27 espie Exp $

